@startuml
participant Visitor
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant EmailService as "Supabase Email"
participant DB as "Postgres/Prisma"

Visitor -> Frontend: Fill register form (name,email,password,confirm)
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/auth/register
Backend -> DB: create user (email_verified=false)
Backend -> EmailService: send verification email with token
EmailService -> Visitor: deliver email (user clicks link)
Visitor -> Frontend: GET /auth/verify-email?token=...
Frontend -> Backend: GET /api/auth/verify-email?token=...
Backend -> DB: validate token, set user.email_verified=true
Backend -> Frontend: 200 OK (account activated)
Frontend -> Visitor: Show success and link to login
@enduml